		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Preferably you want to do it on a board and not 'dead bug' it.  You can buy cheap 4x6 CM 'prototype' boards on ebay.<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.ebay.com/itm/Lot-5pcs-4cmx6cm-Double-side-Protoboard-Circuit-Fibre-Glass-Prototype-PCB-Board-/281357796654?pt=LH_DefaultDomain_0&amp;hash=item41823b452e">http://www.ebay.com/itm/Lot-5pcs-4cmx6c ... 41823b452e</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Of course you only need 6 rows x 6 columns, so just cut it to size.<br /><br />Alternatively, people sell them pre-assembled on ebay, but at a grossly overpriced cost.

		

